18.i. 'Admin option' and 'Grant option' diffrence ? 

=> ✅ ADMIN OPTION – for System Privileges

		👉 This allows a user to not only use the system privilege, but also grant it to 
			others.
		👉 GRANT CREATE USER TO 'HR' WITH ADMIN OPTION;

		📌 HR can create users.
		📌 HR can also run:  'GRANT CREATE USER TO 'HR1';
		

	✅ GRANT OPTION – for Object Privileges.

		👉 This allows a user to use an object (like a table) and give access to others too.
		👉 GRANT SELECT ON hr.employees TO 'HR1' WITH GRANT OPTION;

		📌 HR can read from the hr.employees table.
		📌 HR can also run:  GRANT SELECT ON hr.employees TO bob;

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


